Bart-
You will need to install the oil tank
( 911 is dry sump system )
in the right rear corner. It's a snug
but good fit, and will have to be
notched in (remove the battery
plate) and relocate the battery
to the other side. You will also
need aftermarket air cleaners.
Dave \X/

